premise_source_doc_sentence: Robb Stark is a fictional character in the A Song of Ice and Fire series of fantasy novels by American author George R. R. Martin , and its television adaptation Game of Thrones .
Introduced in 1996 's A Game of Thrones , Robb is the eldest son of Eddard Stark , the honorable lord of Winterfell , an ancient fortress in the North of the fictional continent Westeros .
He subsequently appeared in Martin 's A Clash of Kings  (  1998  )  and A Storm of Swords  (  2000  )  .
Robb is portrayed by Richard Madden in the HBO television adaptation .
